{
  "stem": "20088.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 23.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, she couldn't-- so she saw how I had to kneel with this stool on top off me, and you know, diarrhea, and everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was-- I mean, that was the beginning of my camp life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But those toilet facilities and washing facilities, that was as well a big barrack.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were holds, 50 holds, on each side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the middle was a platform where a capo walked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to sit on this-- sort of on this hole.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember my father saying, you must never sit on it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I tried to kind of not to sit, and to stand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But this capo walked on there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if she saw somebody was not sitting, she hit you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had no toilet paper, nothing, so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the washing, that was another block where there were, again, a long row, with taps, and basins, and with a little bit of water.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just trickled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't much water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And 500 people wanted to go at this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was very limited washing facilities at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and for three weeks, we were in quarantine with just doing appell, getting our food, and not doing anything for three weeks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we just talked what we were going to do, and how life was going to be, and nothing really happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, long days were very long.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in a way, we longed to get out and do something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, the capo came, and said, today, you all stand in a row.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you're going to be sorted out into work commandos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they-- the Germans did that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the SS came, and walked in front of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I looked a bit better than most, because I had my hair.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
